Found: <rs type="found">north of the Museum, south of the <rs type="monuList">City, Water Channel area</rs> excavations.</rs>
; Last known location: <rs type="lastLocation">behind the dighouse (Sebasteion entrance); has a painted 230 on it</rs>
</p>
</div>
